    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Demonheart: The Cursed Trial</i> is an otome visual novel set in a dark fantasy world of demons and magic. Step into the boots of one with a demonic heart and join the twisted game of romance and betrayal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364560/extras/6397fed237b49765dfd7e7da797ea0a3.avif?t=1748364077\" width=620 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Female protagonist </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hundreds of conversation choices - you pick nearly every line the main character says </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Two human male love interests (Ran and Kaisar), some flirting with a female human (Vita) and a male demonspawn </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > An alignment system - you can play as Good, Evil, Tactful, Defiant or in between</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Customizable name </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A dark story full of mystery and deceit </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some lines of dialogue are voiced over</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Bad guys and plot twists :)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364560/extras/30ac095da873f02f8dfb984d52fa1c63.avif?t=1748364077\" width=620 height=158 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364560/extras/f8e5a93f88f28da729515df3dd529e18.avif?t=1748364077\" width=620 height=80 /></span>You wake up in a strange place, only to realize you have been abducted with seven other people. A city guard, a royal soldier, a witch, a bard, a librarian and two criminals - all captured and brought together by an Infernal force.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A demonspawn appears, delivering a chilling message: there are demonhearts among you - people blessed with regeneration, but cursed to be hunted by everyone else. You are one of them, and you'll do anything to keep your secret safe.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As tensions rise and trust erodes, mysterious deaths start to occur. Can you trust anyone? In this chaos, you may find yourself drawn to one of your fellow captives.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you survive the demonspawn's trial? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2364560/extras/1f6121c017255d81f07d46da8e269f1c.avif?t=1748364077\" width=620 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This game is set in the <strong>Demonheart</strong> universe, but knowledge of the other Demonheart games is not needed to enjoy the story.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
